<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>The worst place in the island! This place is a chiquero (a dump). The room was dark. The A/C unit didn't work, in fact it leaked onto the carpet. WE HAD TO BUY A FAN to circulate the little cold air the a/c provided!! There's only 1 cook for everyone. which meant 1 hour waiting time for your food! (fun guy though, the cook; he's the only good thing about the place)You never see the manager, only some girl who can only say I'm sorry ma'am! The pool!! LORD!!!! No chance I was getting in there!! The water was GREEN and it had nothing to do with the tiles underneath!The furniture looked like it had been salvaged from a flood years ago!The room smelled like it hadn't been opened in years!OHH!! And there's no parking!!! Only some pebbled lot with no lines! You have to leave your car's plate number in case someone blocks you or you're blocking them!!!Let me tell you, I don't drink, but after 2 hours in that place, I was ready to drink my sorrows away!They refused to give back my money... (they say no refunds when you call and reserve!! They're not dumb!)They should shut down the place!! It's also infested with pigeons... there were pigeon feathers all around the pool and in the water! YUCK!!In short.... DON'T EVER THINK ABOUT STAYING THERE!!! You're better off sleeping in your car!(I don't have fotos because I haven't developed them yet! But I will!! I took pictures!) 
